└── README.md

Setup Instructions
1. Start Airflow Environment
docker-compose -f docker-compose-mlflow.yaml up
This starts:

Airflow scheduler
Airflow webserver
PostgreSQL backend
dbt-enabled Airflow container
2. Configure Airflow Connection
In Airflow UI:

Create connection: snowflake_conn
Required fields:
Account
User
Password
Database
Schema
Warehouse
Role
This connection is used by the dbt DAG.

3. Verify dbt Setup
Inside the Airflow container:

dbt debug --profiles-dir /opt/airflow/dbt --project-dir /opt/airflow/dbt

Running the Pipeline
Run via Airflow UI
Open Airflow Web UI
Find DAG: Open Meteo and BuildELT_dbt
Trigger DAG manually
The DAG executes:

dbt run
dbt test
dbt snapshot
